# Changelog

## v0.3.0 - Feb 21, 2023

- Fixed missing frontend assets

## v0.2.1 - Feb 14, 2023

- Changed `st_cache` to `st_cache_data`-

## v0.2.0 - Oct 12, 2022

## v0.1.0 - Oct 11, 2022

- Initial release
- Added support for vis.js timeline
